thread.title_full: Prudent Financial Services reviewed by Jennifer Vassell

author: Jennifer Vassell
title: Jennifer Vassell
text:
My Name is Jennifer V. I have been going to Prudent Financial now a few years. I find Deborah McGee always a great help to me when I need it, she is very understanding and feels my needs, this makes me very comfortable when I need their help.
Thank you Deborah, and all your colleagues at Prudent Financial
Jennifer
